---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — Verto"
  description="How Verto collects, uses, and protects information from visitors to verto.fun."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="prose-verto">

      <h2>What We Collect</h2>
      <p>Verto does not require account registration and does not collect personally identifiable information directly. We use standard web analytics (server logs, aggregate traffic data) to understand site usage. If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address for the purpose of sending editorial updates.</p>

      <h2>Affiliate Links and Third-Party Sites</h2>
      <p>Verto contains affiliate links to third-party products and services. When you click an affiliate link, you are redirected to a third-party website that has its own privacy policy. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those third parties. Advertisers and affiliate networks may set cookies when you visit their sites.</p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>Verto uses minimal first-party cookies for site functionality. Affiliate tracking links may set third-party cookies governed by those networks' privacy policies (MaxBounty and affiliated advertisers). You can disable cookies in your browser settings.</p>

      <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell or rent visitor data. Aggregate analytics data may be shared with service providers for the purpose of operating this site.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy questions: <a href="mailto:hello@verto.fun" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-dark">hello@verto.fun</a></p>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
